{"tid":1936991,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"元朗有警員要求包括用餐在內市民離開 否則屬非法集結","createTime":"2020-03-21T15:07:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-22T16:00:16.000Z","uid":25468,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b91ad1fa76fd5c632a50d8a177909b48d9ba712a","tid":1936991,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T15:07:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1516019_1_L_20200321222717.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1516019_1_L_20200321222717.jpg&h=57a5853b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n元朗7.21襲擊事件8個月，有市民響應網上號召到元朗，晚上9時許多名市民在合益路聚集，警方一度舉起藍旗及黑旗，要求市民返回行人路。<br />\n<br />\n有警員用擴音器表示，已經向在場市民給予足夠警告，要求包括在附近食飯的市民離開，否則是未經批准集結，警方會用適當武力將他們移離。<br />\n<br />\n警方晚上近9時，在合益路及又新街交界施放兩枚催淚彈，現場記者未戴上防毒面罩，警員追趕聚集人士，最少4人被制服，警員又向記者舉起胡椒噴霧，多名市民包括義務急救員被防暴警察截查，元朗區議會主席黃偉賢被帶上警車。<br />\n<br />\n較早前，有人在大棠路及教育路交界堵路，將雜物推出馬路，有人點火燒紙皮，又新街一帶亦有人聚集，高叫口號。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1516019-20200321.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1516019-20200321.htm&d=KoefzaQlkmro%2FPgOzv92F%2BzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=fbd0a0f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1516019-20200321.htm&h=80bb19dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1516019-20200321.htm</a>"},{"pid":"5d5e2c60c4bddc7c433b30b0cc0cbf558364af29","tid":1936991,"uid":114814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T15:10:54.000Z","msg":"食飯都犯法。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db14a0e8f21e6fc6dd83e0cba20698f2451f5c2c","tid":1936991,"uid":114814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d5e2c60c4bddc7c433b30b0cc0cbf558364af29","tid":1936991,"uid":114814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T15:10:54.000Z","msg":"食飯都犯法。。<img src